<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zdc1665702915750.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zdc1665702915750.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zdc1665702915750.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zdc1665702915750\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">List of <code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipType</code> structures describing all relations\n    belonging to the current entity.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zdc1665702915750__section_agp_n1r_dwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d238704e53\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The relations of a table are described in two lists of relationship structures. These lists\n        are available through the <code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipInfoType</code>. Connectors can access the\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipInfoType</code> structure by means of the address available in\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;umisc</code> in the Open mode 4, 5 and 6.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Elements</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__1\">Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__2\">Element </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__3\">Description </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipType</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">*OneRelationshipList</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__3\">An array of <code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipType</code>\n                structures describing the relationships in which the table described by the current\n                control block has the ‘one’ role. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">int</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">OneRelationships</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__3\"> Number of elements in the\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">OneRelationshipList</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipType</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">*ManyRelationshipList</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__3\"> An array of <code class=\"ph codeph\">RelationshipType</code>\n                structures describing the relationships in which the table described by the current\n                control block has the ‘many’ role.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">int</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">ManyRelationships</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zdc1665702915750__table_d15416e1_d15417e1_d15418e1__entry__3\"> Number of elements in the\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">ManyRelationshipList</code> . </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534398\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534398\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "RelationshipInfoType Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 List of RelationshipType structures describing all relations belonging to the current entity. Description The relations of a table are described in two lists of relationship structures. These lists are available through the RelationshipInfoType . Connectors can access the RelationshipInfoType structure by means of the address available in uctrl->umisc in the Open mode 4, 5 and 6. Table 1. Elements Type Element Description RelationshipType *OneRelationshipList An array of RelationshipType structures describing the relationships in which the table described by the current control block has the ‘one’ role. int OneRelationships Number of elements in the OneRelationshipList . RelationshipType *ManyRelationshipList An array of RelationshipType structures describing the relationships in which the table described by the current control block has the ‘many’ role. int ManyRelationships Number of elements in the ManyRelationshipList . Related Links uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}